rows.label: qst101802_msg001
rows.name: Temp implementation of LIST_QST101802

rows.label: qst101802_msg002
rows.name:
I'm saved, mo~! I was
attacked while gathering
supplies and froze up, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg003
rows.name:
...But it's been days since
then, and she might have
collapsed from worry, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg004
rows.name:
She should be in the
Mercenary Village, so
please take Jizo to her, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0001
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Phew!!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0002
rows.name: Lots of food, mo! Time to eat, mo!!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0003
rows.name: Phew~! My tummy is full, mo~!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0004
rows.name: I'm late in introducing myself, mo~

rows.label: qst101802_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm the Driver, Jizo, mo~!
Thanks to you, I was saved, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0006
rows.name:
I wandered into this place
full of strong monsters...

rows.label: qst101802_msg0007
rows.name:
I was so scared that I didn't
move, and dust piled up on me,
making me look like a statue...

rows.label: qst101802_msg0008
rows.name:
My tummy was rumbling, and I
was completely stuck, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0009
rows.name:
Thank you, mo~! Both Jizo and
my Blade are saved... mo?

rows.label: qst101802_msg0010
rows.name:
Mo~? She's not here, mo~?
Where did Vahsah go, mo~?

rows.label: qst101802_msg0011
rows.name: Jizo's Blade, Vahsah, is missing, mo~

rows.label: qst101802_msg0012
rows.name:
Maybe she went to Jizo's friend in
Hræsvelgr to ask for help, mo...?

rows.label: qst101802_msg0013
rows.name: Please, mo~ Take Jizo to Hræsvelgr, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0014
rows.name:
Without a Blade, I don't think I
can get back in one piece, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0015
rows.name: Thank you, mo~

rows.label: qst101802_msg0016
rows.name:
My friend... It's been a while
since I've seen Possah, mo.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0017
rows.name:
I've lost a little weight, so
she might be surprised, mo.
